snippet.title: Deltarune Rouxls Kaard - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Rouxls Kaard is finally out! (Volume may need to be adjusted)

REMINDER: Rouxls Kaard is a CYF (Create Your Frisk) Mod and must have the proper engine to be downloaded. Check the Gamejolt tab for information on how to download CYF
Play the game here: https://gamejolt.com/games/deltarunerouxlskaard/839713

Music by Mr.Stardust
Deltarune and all associated characters by Toby Fox
Trailer production by TimberWolfStudios
